Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.21,0:00:07.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Fushi muncul di samping Mizuha yang hilang.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.67,0:00:09.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.71,0:00:12.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tetap di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.88,0:00:14.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gadis itu bernama Mizuha.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.51,0:00:17.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kehidupannya yang biasa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.51,0:00:19.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bergema dengan suara kehancuran
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.89,0:00:23.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}di tempat yang luput dari pengamatan Fushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.44,0:00:29.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.37,0:02:06.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku merasakan sakit yang luar biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.29,0:02:09.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa yang melakukan ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.76,0:02:17.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini aroma Mizuha.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.09,0:02:18.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu dia…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.38,0:02:22.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada yang bisa kubantu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.76,0:02:24.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadilah…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.97,0:02:26.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}temanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.94,0:02:31.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu. Itu tidak sulit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.73,0:02:38.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cobalah berdiri. Bisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.37,0:02:44.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ada orang yang kau percayai?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.74,0:02:46.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo ke rumah ayahmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.58,0:02:47.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kuantar kau ke sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.50,0:02:48.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak mau!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.62,0:02:50.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan ditangkap polisi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.54,0:02:52.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak menginginkan itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.33,0:02:53.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, aku takkan sempurna.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.55,0:02:57.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Polisi? Apa mereka orang yang menakutkan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.38,0:03:02.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seharusnya kau tahu aku membunuh ibuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.39,0:03:07.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak mau masa depanku\Nditentukan oleh orang lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.81,0:03:11.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong selamatkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.56,0:03:14.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana aku bisa menyelamatkanmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.48,0:03:16.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sembunyikan aku!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.24,0:03:27.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pakailah sepatu ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.50,0:03:30.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini sepatu yang aneh, tapi terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.46,0:03:34.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.71,0:03:38.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku belum bertanya. Siapa namamu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.63,0:03:40.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namaku…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.55,0:03:41.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Fushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.47,0:03:43.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar, kan? Aku membacanya di buku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.09,0:03:47.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kau pikir aku tidak sadar\Nkau menyembunyikan kekuatanmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.39,0:03:49.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku.\NKukira aku menyembunyikannya dengan baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.07,0:03:59.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak akan ada yang datang ke sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.91,0:04:11.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sungguh akan tinggal di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.00,0:04:12.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sampai kapan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.92,0:04:14.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bisa membuat kasur?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.67,0:04:16.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.95,0:04:21.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa tidak ada listrik di sini,\Njadi, siapkan lilin juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.47,0:04:23.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisa buat pemantik atau korek api?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.97,0:04:25.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pemantik? Korek api?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.80,0:04:27.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan bilang kau tidak tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.89,0:04:29.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pergi dan carilah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.60,0:04:32.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bisa membuat salinan apa pun\Nyang pernah kau sentuh, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.31,0:04:36.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selain itu, pakaian dan handuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.23,0:04:38.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sabun, sampo, kondisioner,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.77,0:04:40.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan pengering rambut.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.73,0:04:42.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak ada listrik di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.11,0:04:45.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bahkan tidak bisa membuat\Nminuman panas dengan ketel listrik.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.53,0:04:47.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak yakin apa itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.24,0:04:48.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan mencarinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.70,0:04:51.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu, mari bicarakan itu besok.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.41,0:04:54.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisakah kau menemaniku malam ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.50,0:04:55.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku takut.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.48,0:05:20.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah selesai.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.44,0:05:25.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, apa rencanamu besok?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.53,0:05:27.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin akan masuk berita besok.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.78,0:05:30.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, sidik jariku ada di mana-mana.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.20,0:05:33.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja, aku juga tidak bisa bersekolah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.04,0:05:35.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kau…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.46,0:05:38.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Fushi, kau tinggal di rumah Yuki, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.13,0:05:41.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kau datang ke kota ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.00,0:05:43.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kebetulan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.21,0:05:45.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika harus kukatakan,\Nmungkin karena tempat ini tampak damai.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.72,0:05:47.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kau juga kebetulan bertemu denganku?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.01,0:05:49.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sulit mengatakannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.72,0:05:51.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mizuha, kenapa kau…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.56,0:05:53.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku lapar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.68,0:05:54.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.98,0:05:57.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Luar biasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.27,0:05:59.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bisa membuat apa pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.23,0:06:00.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makanlah dahulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.06,0:06:02.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, selamat makan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.28,0:06:10.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Fushi, kau punya makanan favorit?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.78,0:06:12.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin daging.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.66,0:06:14.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Belakangan ini, aku suka itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.16,0:06:15.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tahu teh boba?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.95,0:06:19.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini mengingatkanku\Npada telur yang pernah kulihat di rawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.42,0:06:21.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak pernah membayangkan\Nrasanya selezat ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.04,0:06:23.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Telur?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.17,0:06:26.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan, itu terbuat dari pati.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.84,0:06:29.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, ini bahan modern.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.84,0:06:31.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dunia ini luas sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.55,0:06:34.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wajar jika aku tidak tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.18,0:06:37.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Fushi manis sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.39,0:06:41.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kau membunuh ibumu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.69,0:06:44.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.15,0:06:47.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak ingat membunuh siapa pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.65,0:06:51.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya ingat merasa kecewa pada ibuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.87,0:06:56.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu memberiku\Naksesori rambutnya yang berharga.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.25,0:06:59.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi itu bohong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.16,0:07:00.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aksesori rambut pemberian Ibu
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.79,0:07:04.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dijual seharga 300 yen di toko terdekat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.50,0:07:08.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah itu berarti\Nkau sangat penting bagi ibumu,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.76,0:07:10.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sampai dia bersedia berbohong padamu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.88,0:07:12.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia hanya asal bicara.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.85,0:07:15.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika aku penting baginya,\Ndia tak mungkin bohong padaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.51,0:07:18.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitukah? Apa seperti itu…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.14,0:07:23.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak mau\Nada yang melihatku saat aku tidur.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.27,0:07:24.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau juga harus tidur.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.48,0:07:25.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pejamkanlah matamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.40,0:07:27.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.61,0:07:34.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Fushi, kau pernah bertemu leluhurku, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.83,0:07:37.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku keturunan Hayase.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.04,0:07:40.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu sebabnya kau peduli padaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.50,0:07:42.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seperti apa dia?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.50,0:07:43.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seperti apa dia…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.38,0:07:47.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia orang yang baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.55,0:07:48.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seberapa baik?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.63,0:07:54.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia tampaknya mengurusku dengan baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.76,0:07:56.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia memberiku makanan lezat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.64,0:07:59.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia kuat dan baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.39,0:08:02.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia sering membantu orang lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.19,0:08:04.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia menghargai ikatan keluarga.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.69,0:08:07.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia dikelilingi banyak teman…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.36,0:08:08.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bohong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.98,0:08:10.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak berbohong!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.19,0:08:12.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tidak memejamkan matamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.40,0:08:14.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Itu maksudmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.45,0:08:19.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di dunia yang damai ini,\Nmasih ada seorang gadis malang.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.04,0:08:23.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak bisa tidur nyenyak\Nsampai kau tertidur.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.75,0:08:30.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Matamu sudah terpejam?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.97,0:08:33.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.15,0:08:47.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat pagi. Sarapan sudah siap.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.48,0:08:52.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bermimpi ibuku pergi dan aku sendirian.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.44,0:08:55.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat tahu itu benar, aku merasa putus asa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.03,0:08:59.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kurasa dunia nyata lebih bahagia
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.41,0:09:03.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}karena aku melihat Fushi begitu terbangun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.29,0:09:07.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan mencarikan kebutuhanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.33,0:09:10.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pemantik, sampo, dan kondisioner.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.55,0:09:13.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika semua lancar,\Naku akan bawa kembali ibumu juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.30,0:09:16.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biar kulihat apa aku bisa\Nmenghidupkannya kembali.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.30,0:09:17.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu sebentar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.80,0:09:18.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebentar…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.85,0:09:19.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Sebentar"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.60,0:09:23.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggulah sebentar lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.52,0:09:24.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika ibumu masih hidup,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.89,0:09:26.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kau bisa bersekolah
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.35,0:09:28.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan tidak akan ditangkap polisi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.27,0:09:29.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semuanya akan beres.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.82,0:09:31.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa maksudmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.57,0:09:33.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku membunuh ibuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.69,0:09:35.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kau tidak ingat, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.61,0:09:36.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin itu bukan salahmu…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.78,0:09:37.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.95,0:09:40.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jasadnya mungkin sudah ditemukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.95,0:09:43.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi bukankah lebih baik\Njika dia masih hidup?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.25,0:09:44.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.46,0:09:47.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kumohon, tunggu sebentar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.71,0:09:50.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untuk saat ini, demi aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.17,0:09:54.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mengerti.\NAku akan menuruti perkataanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.30,0:09:56.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.88,0:09:58.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, aku akan cari yang kau mau.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.01,0:10:01.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku segera kembali.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.68,0:10:03.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan menunggu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.22,0:10:06.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.56,0:10:08.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bon, di mana kau?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.48,0:10:10.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.65,0:10:14.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bon pergi rapat dengan Yayasan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.23,0:10:15.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada keributan apa pagi-pagi sekali?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.99,0:10:17.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mau uang.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.36,0:10:21.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah kau membawa 100.000\Ndari Yayasan tempo hari?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.62,0:10:23.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau mau ke rumah bordil lagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.54,0:10:26.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, aku menemukan tempat\Nuntuk bertaruh pacuan kuda.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.08,0:10:28.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau mau ikut?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.17,0:10:32.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat mendengar caramu mati\Ndi kehidupanmu sebelumnya,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.92,0:10:34.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku hanya bisa mengesah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.96,0:10:37.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kurasa caramu mati\Ndi kehidupan ini juga akan sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.80,0:10:42.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kapan kau belajar\Nbicara seperti itu kepadaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.10,0:10:43.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak ingat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.47,0:10:44.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau ingin berkelahi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.06,0:10:47.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aiko, aku memecahkan semua telurnya…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.81,0:10:50.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Rasakan ini!\N- Sama sekali tidak sakit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.65,0:10:55.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Pak Tua! Berkelahi\Ndi depan anak-anak itu memalukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.44,0:10:57.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku belum tua!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.40,0:11:00.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pak Tua, masih terlalu pagi\Nuntuk keributan ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.16,0:11:04.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo ke mal setelah makan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.79,0:11:06.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kakek, bolehkah?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.79,0:11:07.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.91,0:11:10.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah! Kami juga mau pergi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.62,0:11:11.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Fushi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.54,0:11:12.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Fushi, kau sudah pulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.04,0:11:13.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.96,0:11:15.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau juga akan berbelanja?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.63,0:11:16.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.71,0:11:19.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gawat, kita tidak punya uang.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.51,0:11:22.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tenang. Akan kuhasilkan\Nsebanyak yang kita butuhkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.55,0:11:23.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Serahkan padaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.80,0:11:25.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Tidak boleh!\N- Kenapa tidak?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.81,0:11:27.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan begini,\Naku tidak akan menyusahkanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.02,0:11:29.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kubilang tidak boleh, jadi, tidak!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.60,0:11:32.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau akan membuat uangnya\Nkehilangan nilainya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.44,0:11:33.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kehilangan nilainya?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.27,0:11:37.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan membagi uang sakuku dengan kalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.28,0:11:42.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masing-masing 300…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.41,0:11:43.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dua ratus…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.07,0:11:46.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, 300 saja…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.95,0:11:48.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.41,0:11:52.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa aku menjadi orang dewasa yang buruk?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.25,0:11:56.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku membuat gadis semuda itu menangis…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.21,0:11:59.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan membalas kebaikanmu\Ndengan setumpuk uang!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.51,0:12:03.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan mencari pekerjaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.89,0:12:08.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menurut March, ini lebih bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.18,0:12:09.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku senang sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.85,0:12:11.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah lama aku tidak ke toko pakaian.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.89,0:12:13.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada rok yang serasi di sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.94,0:12:16.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ini gaya yang disukai gadis zaman ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.19,0:12:17.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Atau mungkin ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.69,0:12:19.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pakaian pria ada di sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.24,0:12:21.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.57,0:12:25.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku juga ingin memakai\Npakaian manis saat menjadi gadis!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.16,0:12:28.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.04,0:12:37.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setidaknya aku harus minta maaf\Nkepada Ayah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.88,0:12:43.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Halo, Ayah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.51,0:12:46.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mizuha, di mana kau sekarang?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.39,0:12:51.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku.\NAku tidak menduga ini akan terjadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.89,0:12:53.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pulanglah sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.64,0:12:55.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibumu sangat mencemaskanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.44,0:12:58.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu dan Ayah tidak marah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.65,0:13:00.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pulang saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.07,0:13:02.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.58,0:13:11.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mizuha, kau sudah pulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.41,0:13:13.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau dari mana saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.46,0:13:15.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sudah sarapan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.33,0:13:18.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Duduklah dahulu. Mari bicara sambil makan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.38,0:13:23.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Kau punya pakaian ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.55,0:13:25.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Atau Hanna yang meminjamkannya padamu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.93,0:13:31.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mizuha, sepertinya ibumu\Ningin mengatakan sesuatu kepadamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.35,0:13:32.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sayang, katakanlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.56,0:13:33.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.48,0:13:34.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mizuha, maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.98,0:13:40.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat kau pergi ke rumah Kakek,\Nkupikir kau membenciku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.86,0:13:45.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, aku sengaja menyembunyikan\Nikat rambutmu agar kau menyukaiku lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.28,0:13:46.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga berbohong kepadamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.87,0:13:50.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tidak pulang kemarin\Nkarena tahu soal ini, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.29,0:13:54.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mulai sekarang, aku akan berusaha\Nmembuatmu memercayaiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.16,0:13:57.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak apa-apa jika kau tidak mau belajar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.46,0:13:59.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pergilah bermain saat kau mau.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.38,0:14:03.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu, kemarin aku…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.01,0:14:07.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}membunuh…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.13,0:14:09.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku membunuh Ibu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.76,0:14:12.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benarkah?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.14,0:14:14.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau pasti bermimpi buruk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.02,0:14:18.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku.\NAku pasti membuatmu terlalu stres.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.35,0:14:20.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mimpi buruk?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.27,0:14:21.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo makan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.61,0:14:24.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku membuat jamuan hanya untukmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.05,0:14:28.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mimori, ayo pulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.91,0:14:30.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu, aku mau camilan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.74,0:14:32.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masih ada camilan yang kemarin dibeli, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.87,0:14:34.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan membelikannya untukmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.20,0:14:36.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berhentilah menatap orang lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.00,0:14:39.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo. Waktunya makan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.84,0:14:48.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibumu masih hidup?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.68,0:14:50.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku belum melakukan apa pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.76,0:14:54.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi dia memasak di rumah\Ndan menungguku seperti biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.64,0:14:58.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sungguh melihat jasad ibumu kemarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.35,0:15:00.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bahkan mengatakannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.77,0:15:02.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Aku membunuh Ibu."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.56,0:15:05.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi dia bilang,\N"Kau pasti bermimpi buruk."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.95,0:15:10.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan pulang hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.28,0:15:14.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku datang untuk mengatakan itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.16,0:15:15.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan ke sekolah besok.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.74,0:15:17.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.96,0:15:19.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, untuk saat ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.42,0:15:23.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang harus kulakukan\Ndengan pakaian dan pemantik ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.59,0:15:25.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Simpan saja untuk saat ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.59,0:15:27.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, masalahnya belum selesai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.80,0:15:31.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, mari bertemu di sini\Nsetiap hari sepulang sekolah
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.97,0:15:33.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan bicara baik-baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.64,0:15:35.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.56,0:15:36.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sampai jumpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.27,0:15:39.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar juga!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.43,0:15:41.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku boleh memanggilmu Fushi, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.56,0:15:43.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.32,0:15:48.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.36,0:15:53.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sudah memakainya?\NCocok untukmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.12,0:15:58.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pakaian modern memang sangat modis.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.20,0:16:01.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu juga sangat cocok untukmu, Kai.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.50,0:16:04.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, kau dari mana saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.50,0:16:06.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah kita selesai berbelanja,\Nkau tiba-tiba menghilang.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.13,0:16:07.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau membuatku takut.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.51,0:16:10.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang kau lihat?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.84,0:16:13.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kau berpakaian seperti itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.14,0:16:15.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sama sekali tidak cocok untukmu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.85,0:16:18.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, ini cocok untukku!\NIni sangat cocok denganku!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.39,0:16:20.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sama sekali tidak terlihat manis.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.35,0:16:22.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika kau terus memakai\Npakaian berenda seperti ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.90,0:16:24.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku bisa mati tertawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.35,0:16:27.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini yang dipilih March untukku!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.11,0:16:31.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Minta maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.15,0:16:32.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.07,0:16:34.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang lebih tulus.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.07,0:16:37.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kata-katamu kejam!\NKau membuatku sedih!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.53,0:16:40.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kau mengatakan hal sekasar itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.20,0:16:42.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, maafkan aku. Tolong maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.96,0:16:44.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sungguh minta maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.25,0:16:45.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Kau tak bisa hanya minta maaf.\N- 999 Legenda Urban Dunia
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.79,0:16:47.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Katakanlah\N- berturutan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.34,0:16:48.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- kesalahanmu!\N- Berisik!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.34,0:16:50.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- TV-nya tak terdengar.\N- Inilah nomor 98!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.51,0:16:52.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pemuda yang sangat kuat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.59,0:16:54.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pemuda ini ditabrak truk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.51,0:16:56.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua orang mengira dia sudah mati.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.68,0:16:59.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Itu aku.\N- Ada kasus serupa di seluruh dunia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.06,0:17:01.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pria yang jatuh dari jembatan…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.60,0:17:08.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu bukan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.48,0:17:10.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin itu dibuat dengan CGI.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.35,0:17:15.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kapan Bon kembali?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.06,0:17:19.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entahlah. Kurasa dia\Ntidak akan kembali untuk sementara.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.36,0:17:21.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau mencarinya?\NPerlu kutelepon dan tanyakan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.57,0:17:22.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak perlu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.07,0:17:25.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa Tuan Messar baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.57,0:17:27.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia hanya punya 500 yen…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.50,0:17:29.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia akan baik-baik saja selama menang judi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.84,0:17:34.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian berdua seharusnya cukup dewasa\Nuntuk memakai sumpit dan sendok.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.34,0:17:35.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sumpit?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.34,0:17:38.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maksudmu ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.31,0:17:44.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di mana pria dari Yanome itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.64,0:17:47.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maksudmu Kahaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.27,0:17:48.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa dia tidak ada di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.06,0:17:50.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di mana dia?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.27,0:17:51.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Fu, beri tahu aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.69,0:17:55.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bon tak memberitahuku apa pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.99,0:17:57.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu pula siapa pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.24,0:18:00.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa begitulah adanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.41,0:18:02.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kahaku tidak bersamaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.16,0:18:05.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia tidak di sini.\NDia memilih pergi ke tempat lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.29,0:18:08.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa itu yang terbaik.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.71,0:18:10.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau mencemaskannya?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.09,0:18:10.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.00,0:18:15.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena kurasa dia salah satu dari kita.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.72,0:18:18.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.97,0:18:21.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kuharap dia baik-baik saja di tempat lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.26,0:18:23.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.06,0:18:25.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.31,0:18:32.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mizuha, selamat pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.11,0:18:34.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sayang, ini berlebihan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.40,0:18:35.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tidak akan memotret?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.90,0:18:37.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah selesai memotret.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.61,0:18:38.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.91,0:18:41.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena aku ibu yang baru sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.04,0:18:46.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak bisa makan banyak\Npagi-pagi sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.41,0:18:47.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.00,0:18:50.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia benar-benar hidup.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.29,0:18:54.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, ini jenis pakaian yang kau suka.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.09,0:18:55.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.01,0:18:57.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan mencobanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.59,0:18:59.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan mengintip.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.60,0:19:05.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu Mizuha tampak nyata.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.60,0:19:09.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa dia hidup kembali tanpa kekuatanku?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.44,0:19:12.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Atau itu orang lain? Peniru?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.73,0:19:15.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin Mizuha bertemu Bon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.57,0:19:18.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untuk memeriksa apakah ada fye.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.66,0:19:20.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lihat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.37,0:19:22.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.49,0:19:24.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.41,0:19:25.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan hanya bilang "ya".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.91,0:19:27.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bertanya apa ini cocok untukku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.66,0:19:28.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.79,0:19:30.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ini manis?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.21,0:19:31.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.67,0:19:32.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau menyukainya?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.96,0:19:33.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.96,0:19:39.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau mau datang ke rumahku?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.47,0:19:42.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ke rumah Fushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.18,0:19:44.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.22,0:19:47.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi Yuki ada di rumah, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.68,0:19:49.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memangnya kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.56,0:19:52.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin memperkenalkanmu kepada semuanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.48,0:19:55.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kantong ini
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.57,0:19:58.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- yang terakhir!\N- Akarnya tumbuh lebih lambat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.69,0:20:01.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Tapi ada lebih banyak hari ini.\N- Ini dia!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.53,0:20:04.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yuki, aku akan ke rumahmu lusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.66,0:20:08.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau ingat, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.25,0:20:11.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentang makan hot pot bersama, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.00,0:20:13.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hore, hot pot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.58,0:20:16.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah lama kau tidak memakai\Naksesori rambut bulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.80,0:20:17.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Manis sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.92,0:20:19.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.09,0:20:21.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebelumnya hilang,\Ntapi dia sudah menemukannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.47,0:20:22.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini bukan untuk hot pot,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.55,0:20:24.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi untuk menemui Fushi, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.72,0:20:26.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga tertarik.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.39,0:20:27.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boleh aku ikut?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.06,0:20:30.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita pergi lain kali saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.14,0:20:32.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akan merepotkan\Njika terlalu banyak yang datang.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.23,0:20:36.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benda Hitam, bagaimana menurutmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.90,0:20:39.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pernah melihat Nokker\Nyang mampu mengendalikan jasad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.11,0:20:44.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku tak merasakan hal aneh\Ndari ibu Mizuha.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.49,0:20:47.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua Nokker yang bisa kurasakan\Nsudah dimusnahkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.78,0:20:50.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah menancapkan akar\Ndan mencari berulang kali,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.41,0:20:51.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi tidak kutemukan apa pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.96,0:20:54.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu aneh. Apa akarnya tumbuh kembali?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.21,0:20:56.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Apa aku melewatkannya?\N- Kau benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.46,0:20:57.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Ataukah…\N- Baru saja dibuang.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.96,0:20:59.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benda Hitam.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.76,0:21:01.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tahu sesuatu?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.88,0:21:04.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benda Hitam?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.39,0:21:07.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Halo, Semuanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.10,0:21:08.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf mengganggu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.35,0:21:10.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Halo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.27,0:21:12.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Fushi, kau sudah bertemu seniorku, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.77,0:21:13.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mizuha.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.06,0:21:16.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makanannya belum siap.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.31,0:21:17.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Santai saja dan silakan mengobrol.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.15,0:21:19.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.19,0:21:20.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.36,0:21:22.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Senang bertemu kalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.70,0:21:25.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Fushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.66,0:21:27.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkinkah dia Pasukan Pelindung…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.53,0:21:28.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku terkejut kau tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.70,0:21:29.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mata mereka mirip.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.99,0:21:31.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau yang menemukannya?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.58,0:21:32.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.50,0:21:35.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lebih tepatnya,\Ndia kebetulan mengenal Yuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.37,0:21:37.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ini sungguh baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.17,0:21:39.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Fushi, perkenalkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.88,0:21:42.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, aku Tonari.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.80,0:21:44.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini Iddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.22,0:21:45.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka manis sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.76,0:21:46.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa mereka tetanggamu?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.93,0:21:48.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitulah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.60,0:21:50.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, siapa gadis itu bagi Fushi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.01,0:21:52.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana aku tahu?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.31,0:21:54.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suara apa itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.35,0:21:55.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu suara beruang.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.56,0:21:57.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Beruang? Ada beruang piaraan di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.48,0:21:59.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Fu, lihat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.61,0:22:02.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mencabut semua duri dari Tuan Beruang.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.23,0:22:03.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang ia bebas!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.69,0:22:05.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}March, kau luar biasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.40,0:22:06.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.66,0:22:09.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa nona ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.20,0:22:12.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku Mizuha. Fushi dan aku berteman baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.41,0:22:14.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah, Semuanya. Berkumpul.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.16,0:22:16.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Berbarislah.\N- Bon, aku sudah menunggumu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.50,0:22:18.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Kubilang…\N- Tunggu, Fushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.00,0:22:21.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan khawatir. Semuanya dapat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.55,0:22:23.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini Kartu Hijau.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.88,0:22:26.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini KTP untuk dunia ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.51,0:22:33.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saatnya mempertimbangkan\Nmasa depan semua orang di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.35,0:22:36.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekolah, pekerjaan, dan pajak.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.10,0:22:37.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian semua harus lakukan hal ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.90,0:22:38.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.90,0:22:42.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika tidak bersekolah,\Nbekerja, atau memenuhi tugas,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.32,0:22:44.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kalian tak bisa bertahan di dunia ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.28,0:22:45.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekolah?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.49,0:22:46.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bekerja?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.45,0:22:47.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pajak?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.99,0:22:50.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa itu? March tak punya hal seperti itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.12,0:22:52.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Apa kita akan mati?\N- Jangan khawatir.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.70,0:22:57.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan kartu ini dan kekuatan Yayasan,\Nsemua akan baik-baik saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.29,0:22:59.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bukan anak kecil lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.75,0:23:01.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau seharusnya sudah siap untuk masuk SD.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.00,0:23:05.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau seusia Yuki, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.26,0:23:06.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, kau harus masuk SMP.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.09,0:23:08.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga harus sekolah?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.47,0:23:10.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kai dan Gugu akan masuk SMA.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.05,0:23:13.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak akan ke mana-mana!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.10,0:23:15.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah, Semuanya. Mari makan dahulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.56,0:23:20.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini bukan waktu yang tepat\Nuntuk membicarakan ibu Mizuha.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.81,0:23:23.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Semuanya akan memulai\N- Iddy juga ingin membantu.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.73,0:23:24.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- kehidupan baru.\N- Kalau begitu, kuserahkan
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.65,0:23:25.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Hei, Fushi.\N- padamu, Iddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.57,0:23:27.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau juga akan bersekolah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.74,0:23:28.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.15,0:23:30.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Fushi juga sekolah?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.24,0:23:31.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Luar biasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.62,0:23:33.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau akan lebih tenang\Njika bersama Mizuha, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.99,0:23:36.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, itu juga\Nyang diinginkan wanita di belakangmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.80,0:24:34.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu Mizuha sudah meninggal.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.01,0:24:39.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu wanita yang hidup kembali itu apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.10,0:24:41.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena tidak mampu mengetahuinya,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.35,0:24:45.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Fushi mulai gelisah dan tidak tenang.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.40,0:24:48.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di tengah kekacauan,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.65,0:24:52.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Fushi memulai kehidupannya di sekolah.
